MZANSI's most  beautiful women came out in numbers at the annual GLAMOUR Women of the Year event last night. TV actress Celeste Khumalo co-hosted the awards with comedian Donovan Goliath. Miss SA Zozibini Tunzi was also in attendance.  This event  takes place each year, where  they celebrate 11 Most GLAMOURous South African women who have obtained profound success for their impact and contribution in their respective fields. They all came wearing their best ensembles from both international and local designers. Winner of the night include media mogul Bonang Matheba, Mihlali Ndamase, Ayanda Thabethe, Melody Molale, Siyanda Dzenga, Blue Mbombo and Johanna Mukoki.    